## Modelos Eloquent

Dominio: `app/Domain/Assistant/Models/`

| Modelo | Tabla | Notas |
|---|---|---|
| `Conversation` | conversations | hasMany sessions, hasMany messages |
| `Session` | sessions | belongsTo conversation, hasMany messages |
| `AssistantMessage` | messages | belongsTo conversation + session; morphMedia (Spatie) |
| `Memory` | memories | belongsTo user |
| `TypeCatalog` | type_catalogs | belongsTo user nullable |
| `AssistantEvent` | events | belongsTo user; hasMany eventReminders |
| `EventReminder` | event_reminders | belongsTo event |
| `AssistantList` | lists | belongsTo user; hasMany listItems; hasMany listShares |
| `ListItem` | list_items | belongsTo list |
| `Expense` | expenses | belongsTo user |
| `Friendship` | friendships | belongsTo requester (user), addressee (user) |
| `FriendLabel` | friend_labels | belongsTo user, belongsTo friendUser |
| `ListShare` | list_shares | belongsTo list; belongsTo sharedWith (user) |
| `ReminderRequest` | reminder_requests | belongsTo sender, receiver (user); belongsTo event nullable |

