## Docker — nuevo servicio

Añadir en `docker-compose.yml`:

```yaml
assistant-worker:
  build:
    context: ./services/assistant-worker
    dockerfile: Dockerfile
  depends_on:
    redis: { condition: service_healthy }
    postgres: { condition: service_healthy }
  env_file: .env
  networks: [backend]
  restart: unless-stopped
```

Crear `services/assistant-worker/` con estructura mínima:
```
services/assistant-worker/
  src/
    index.ts
  package.json
  tsconfig.json
  Dockerfile
```

El `index.ts` solo conecta a Redis y logea "assistant-worker ready". La lógica real llega en etapa 03.

